PLACEHOLDER FOR NAVCORE PRO APK.
Please replace this file with your actual compiled Android APK.

To generate your APK:
1. Go to https://www.pwabuilder.com/
2. Enter your live site URL: https://hemanthporeddy8.github.io/navcore-pro/
3. Click "Build My App" and download the Android package (APK).
4. Rename the downloaded .apk file to 'navcore.apk' and replace this placeholder file.
5. Run your 'auto_deploy.py' script to deploy it live!
